'''Continuum'''是一家[[设计|设计]]和[[创新|创新]]顾问公司，总部位于美国[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]West Newton，同时在美国[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]、意大利[[米兰|米兰]]、中国[[上海|上海]]和韩国[[首尔|首尔]]设有5个工作室。公司的核心领域包括[[工业设计|工业设计]]、设计战略、服务设计、人因工程、[[交互设计|交互设计]]、可持续性设计、机械工程、环境学设计和[[电气工程|电气工程]]。<ref>[http://www.dcontinuum.com/upload/cappage/profile_english_V5.pdf Continuum fact sheet]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

1983年Continuum成立于美国[[波士顿|波士顿]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=4541288 |title=Continuum Private Company info |accessdate=2011-08-03 |archive-date=2011-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110519181652/http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=4541288 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，原名Design Continuum Inc.，其目标十分简单，旨在为企业用户设计产品。自此之后，业务逐渐发展至包括战略和品牌服务以及体验和产品设计。<ref name="bwMasters">{{cite news |last=Hamm |first=Steve |coauthors=Walters, Helen |url=http://www.businessweek.com/innovate/content/jan2008/id20080116_412812.htm?chan=search |title=Masters of Collaboration |publisher=Business Week |date=2008-01-16 |accessdate=2008-02-16 |archive-date=2010-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609010121/http://www.businessweek.com/innovate/content/jan2008/id20080116_412812.htm?chan=search |dead-url=no }}</ref>

公司目前拥有近200人的工作团队分布于全球范围内的5个工作室。<ref name="bwMasters"/>其合作客户涉及医疗、消费品、计算机、汽车、酒店餐饮和金融服务等行业。公司做过的项目包括[[宝洁|宝洁]]的速易洁、<ref>{{cite news |last=Nussbaum |first=Bruce |url=http://www.businessweek.com/@@XFy594cQKXhCRxkA/magazine/content/04_20/b3883001_mz001.htm |title=The Power of Design |publisher=Business Week |date=2004-05-17 |accessdate=2008-02-16}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>[[锐步|锐步]]的Pump<ref>{{cite web | title = Reebok Pump | publisher = Wikipedia | url = http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reebok_Pump | accessdate = 2008-02-07 | archive-date = 2007-11-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071110190326/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reebok_Pump | dead-url = no }}</ref>运动鞋以及麻省理工媒体研究室的100美元笔记本电脑项目初始设计方向等。<ref>{{cite web |title=One Laptop per Chid Progress |publisher=OLPC |url=http://laptop.org/en/vision/progress/index.shtml |accessdate=2008-02-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080206140805/http://laptop.org/en/vision/progress/index.shtml |archivedate=2008-02-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

自2003年以来，公司获得了14次由美国[[商业周刊|商业周刊]]主办，美国工业设计师协会（IDSA）担任评委的IDEA工业设计杰出大奖。<ref>{{cite web | title = Winners Over The Past Five Years | work = IDSA | publisher = BusinessWeek | date = 2007-07-30 | url = http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/07_31/b4044403.htm?chan=search | accessdate = 2008-02-07 | archive-date = 2011-05-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110523065829/http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/07_31/b4044403.htm?chan=search | dead-url = no }}</ref>公司的众多设计师也出现在Daniel H. Pink的著作“A Whole New Mind”中。<ref>{{cite book| last = Pink| first = Dan| title = A Whole New Mind| url = https://archive.org/details/wholenewmindmovi00pink| publisher = Riverhead Books| year = 2005| location = New York| pages = [https://archive.org/details/wholenewmindmovi00pink/page/97 97] }}</ref>2007年夏季，公司主持了美国公共广播电视公司的电视系列节目“Design Squad”的大结局，该节目旨在鼓励儿童以探索工程和设计领域作为职业方向。<ref>{{cite video
| title = http://pbskids.org/designsquad/challenges/s1-ep13.html| medium = TV| publisher = PBS| location = Boston}}</ref>

